Back in Hong Kong, Chan produced a number of action comedy films with his opera school friends Sammo Hung and Yuen Biao.  The three co-starred together for the first time in 1983 in ''[[Project A]]'', which grossed [[Hong Kong dollar|HK$]]19,323,000 and won the Best Action Choreography Award at the third annual [[Hong Kong Film Awards]].<ref>{{cite web
