  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate = 2007-06-07 }}</ref> Over the following five years, the "Three Brothers" appeared in ''[[Wheels on Meals]]'', the original ''[[Lucky Stars]]'' trilogy, and ''[[Dragons Forever]]''.<ref>{{cite web
