  | accessdate = 2007-06-07 }}</ref> In 1985, Chan made the first ''[[Police Story (film)|Police Story]]'' film, a US-influenced action comedy in which Chan performed his own stunts. It was named "Best Movie" at the 1986 Hong Kong Film Awards.<ref>{{cite web
  | last = Mills
