  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate = 2007-06-07 }}</ref> Starting that year, Chan also voiced a fictionalised version of himself in the [[animated series]] ''[[Jackie Chan Adventures]]'', which ran until 2005.<ref>{{cite web
  | title = Voice actors of Jackie Chan Adventures
  | work = Cast list
  | publisher = VoiceChasers
  | date =
  | url = http://voicechasers.com/database/showprod.php?prodid=233
  | format =
