Despite further success with ''[[Shanghai Noon]]'' in 2000 and ''[[Rush Hour 2]]'' in 2001, Chan became frustrated with Hollywood over the limited range of roles and lack of control over the film-making process.<ref name="Obio">{{cite web
  | last = Chan
