  | accessdate = 2007-06-07 }}</ref>

Chan finished filming ''[[Rush Hour 3]]'' in 2007 and has begun work on ''[[The Forbidden Kingdom]]'', his first onscreen collaboration with fellow [[Hong Kong]] actor [[Jet Li]].<ref>{{cite web
  | title = Rush Hour 3 Production Status
